# the data centre is deployed and operated by an external Data Centre Service Provider (DCSP).
The figure depicts a virtualized 5G Core Network (5GC) deployment on external virtualization infrastructure and data centre, showcasing the use of virtualized NFV (NFV) and NFV-based 5G Core Network (5GC) services. The figure highlights the integration of NFV and NFV-based 5G Core Network services, demonstrating the use of virtualized NFV to optimize network performance and reduce costs.
Figure 4.7.2.3.1.1-1: NOP deploys virtualized 5GC NFs on external virtualization infrastructure and data centre
